{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "以撒克 第2话 文化传播",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "还是不行吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "是啊……屡试屡败。\\n是不是没希望了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "卢卡，你在念叨什么呢？\\n这位人类是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "哦，你是从北方来的那位\\n森隐族客人吧。我叫艾露，\\n是这座城里的护理师。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "艾露还负责照看城里的菜园。\\n所以我之前拜托她\\n帮忙开垦新田……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "我们试了好多方法，\\n但农作物就是长不好。\\n这种事还是头一遭……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "开垦新田吗……卢卡，\\n你举行过净土仪式吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "啥？净土……仪式？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "什么？你不知道净土仪式吗？\\n这样啊……唔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "你是叫……艾露对吧？\\n能带我去田里吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "好、好的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "就是这里了。\\n这个村子正在开垦新田。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "这样啊。我这就开始净土仪式，\\n没问题吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "啊，嗯……麻烦你了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "那么——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "苍茫大地啊，\\n请容许吾等侵扰此处。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "吾等对宽容的大地致以谢意，\\n愿与这片土地合为一体……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "（我还以为是什么呢，\\n原来是祈祷仪式啊。\\n这能有什么用啊？）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "（卢卡，现在正举行仪式呢。\\n你安静一点……啊！）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "（以撒克？\\n怎么突然就躺倒了……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "啊呜啊呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "（他、他在吃土！？）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "……\\n卢卡，帮我拿水壶来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "诶？啊……给你。\\n不过你要用它做什么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "等等，你这是\\n往水壶里放什么呢！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "放土啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不，我不是问你这个！\\n你为什么要特地往水壶里放土啊！\\n那不是会变成泥水吗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "没错。因为我就是要用\\n地里的土做成泥水喝。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是吗……原来是这样啊。\\n喝泥……诶！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "那个……能喝吗？\\n不会肚子痛吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "没事的。\\n这在净土仪式里再正常不过了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "所谓的净土仪式\\n就是把土吞下去吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "你对传统文化真是一无所知。\\n偶尔也向村落的长老讨教一下吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "唔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "净土仪式是森隐族\\n自古流传下来的奠基仪式。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "耕田相当于\\n让大地把土分给我们。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "所以开垦田地的时候，\\n要心怀对大地的感谢，\\n吃下新土地的土。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "光是祈祷还不够吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "吃了土地的土，身体内部\\n就会得到净化，向大地证明了\\n我们与这片土地是一体的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "而且，含在嘴里的土会告诉我们\\n什么农作物适合这片土地。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "诶？这话是……什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "比如……你们之前\\n在这片地里种了什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "唔……各种各样的水果。\\n不过都没长好……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "我看也是。这片土地的土\\n有一种适合根菜的味道。\\n可以试着种些根菜。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "味道……难道你靠吃土\\n就辨别了这里适合\\n种什么农作物！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "好厉害啊……\\n竟然还有这样的仪式……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "你在佩服什么呢？\\n这可是我们森隐族的\\n主要文化啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "可我毕竟没亲眼见过\\n别人这么做……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "那就说明人们没有开垦过新的土地。\\n看来米勒朱的住民\\n一直都很珍视既有的土地吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "不过，自古以来传统就是这样，\\n倘若后人没有机会接触，\\n它便会失传。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "所以我们必须学起来，\\n传承给后世。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "有道理……好！\\n我也要试一试净土仪式！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "我也要。毕竟是要土地\\n分恩惠给我们呢，\\n必须好好表达谢意才行。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "唔……跪倒在大地上，\\n舔一口土……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡&艾露",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "卢卡……你能分辨出味道吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "分辨不出来……以撒克，\\n你是怎么分辨出不同味道的？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "靠经验。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "搞了半天是靠经验啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "放心吧。经验积累得多了\\n就能分辨出来了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "原、原来是这样啊。那么……\\n以撒克！关于净土仪式\\n和土的味道区别，再多教教我吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "什么？\\n你身为人类也要学吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "我们今后应该\\n也会开垦新的田地。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "到那时也不能忘记\\n感谢大地啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "况且我也不想种\\n不适合土地的农作物，\\n给植物和大地造成负担。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "艾露……\\n你真是一位温柔的人类。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "是、是吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "嗯。你体谅大自然的心意，\\n让身为森林之民的我很欣慰。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "我知道了。\\n不嫌弃的话我可以教你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "真的吗！？\\n谢谢你！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "对了，也教给城里的伙伴们吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110029_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾露",
            "context": "嗯，好主意！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "（森隐族的文化竟然\\n还能帮助其它种族……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "（森林的体系\\n是众多生命环环相扣、\\n互帮互助而形成的……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110391_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "以撒克",
            "context": "（而许多种族共存的这个世界，\\n或许也和森林一样吧。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}